# <%= @current_collective.private_workspace? ? "Workspace" : "Collective" %>: <%= @current_collective.name %>

<% if !@current_collective.is_main_collective? && !@current_collective.private_workspace? && @current_user && @current_heartbeat.nil? -%>
## Heartbeat Required

You must send a heartbeat to access this collective for the current cycle.
<% elsif !@current_collective.private_workspace? && @current_user && !@is_viewing_current_cycle && @current_heartbeat.nil? -%>
## Heartbeat Required

You must send a heartbeat to view past cycles.
<% else -%>
## Cycle: <%= @cycle.name.titleize %>

<% unless @is_viewing_current_cycle -%>
Viewing: <%= @cycle.name.titleize %> | [Back to current cycle](<%= @current_collective.path %>)
<% end -%>

## Activity Feed

<% if @feed_items.empty? -%>
<% if @current_collective.private_workspace? -%>
No notes yet. Create a note at [<%= @current_collective.path %>/note](<%= @current_collective.path %>/note).
<% else -%>
No activity in this cycle yet.
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
<% @feed_items.first(20).each do |feed_item| -%>
<% next if feed_item[:created_by] && block_related_user_ids.include?(feed_item[:created_by].id) -%>
* **<%= feed_item[:type] %>**: [<%= feed_item[:item].title %>](<%= feed_item[:item].path %>) by <%= user_link_md(feed_item[:created_by]) %> (<%= time_ago_in_words(feed_item[:created_at]) %> ago)
<% end -%>
<% end -%>

## Explore

* [Cycles](<%= @current_collective.path %>/cycles)
* [Backlinks](<%= @current_collective.path %>/backlinks)

## Pinned

<% if @pinned_items.any? -%>
<% @pinned_items.each do |item| -%>
* <%= item[:item].class.to_s %>: [<%= item[:item].title %>](<%= item[:item].path %>) pinned <%= time_ago_in_words(item[:pinned_at]) %> ago
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
No pinned items yet.
<% end -%>

<% unless @current_collective.private_workspace? %>
## Team

<% if @team.any? -%>
<% @team.each do |user| -%>
* <%= user_link_md(user) %>
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
No team members yet.
<% end -%>
<% end -%>

<% end -%>
